; Coverage: value.cc (compare_by_commodity for different commodities
; in is_less_than) and the commodity comparison recursion paths.
; Sorting amounts with different commodities triggers the commodity comparison.

2024/01/01 Buy EUR
    Assets:Foreign    100.00 EUR
    Assets:Cash       $-110.00

2024/01/02 Buy GBP
    Assets:Foreign    50.00 GBP
    Assets:Cash       $-65.00

test reg --sort "amount" Assets:Foreign
24-Jan-01 Buy EUR               Assets:Foreign           100.00 EUR   100.00 EUR
24-Jan-02 Buy GBP               Assets:Foreign            50.00 GBP   100.00 EUR
                                                                       50.00 GBP
end test
